      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>VrS89.20 (mss. 2005, 2007, 2010, 2030, 2040, 2101, 2102, 2104, 2106, 2109, 4010, 4025, 4040, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4161, 4162, 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            zōt <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō yō frabərəta frā.mē mrūte</em> rāspīg pad gāh ī frabardārān <em>aθā ratuš</em> kardan zōt <em>auuaθāt̰ iδā səraōšō astū</em></ab>  
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "The <em>zōt</em> (should recite): <em>yaθā ahū vairiiō yō frabərəta frā.mē mrūte</em>. The <em>rāspīg</em> should answer at the place the <em>frabardārān: aθā ratuš</em>. 
            The <em>zōt</em> (should recite): <em>auuaθāt̰ iδā səraōšō astū</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
